body:
One Click Optimization's main focus is to maximize fps on **low end** systems. Even though my main focus is low end systems, this mod pack still drasticlly increase fps on higher end systems.

# Features;
- 3x fps
- Optimized configs
- QOL mods (Mouse Tweaks)

One Click Optimization will be updated often to keep maximum performance. If mods are not updated soon after a minecraft update release, a beta version of the modpack will release **WITHOUT** all of the mods.

